      <ID>26</ID>
      <DefaultText>This tank contains a humanoid with a skull-like head. A name arises from your inherited memories. This is a nevajin, a creature of relentless, overpowering curiosity. Unaware of the Sorrow fragments roaming the platforms, it speaks to itself in a grinding whisper, in a language you don't understand. 

